www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Madonna-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Madonna-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Madonna-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Madonna-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Madonna-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Madonna-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）</a>超越了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">麦当娜（Madonna）</a> ，成为英国第一张专辑的女性艺术家。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swift-eras-tour-end-impact-3820896">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）的时代之旅结束：看看它的全球影响力</a></strong></li></ul><p>斯威夫特（Swift）用她的最新现场专辑《 Lover（来自巴黎现场）》（Live from Paris）打破了唱片，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-lover-review-2541084">她2019年Studio LP</a>的现场表演，使她的第13位。</p><p>直播乙烯基版本最初是在2023年的情人节限量发行的，但是今年，可提供新的心形双乙烯基版本。该唱片在英国售出了47,000张，使其成为2025年迄今为止专辑最大的开幕周。</p><p>它标志着Swift第二次获得专辑的第一次，而不是流媒体服务，这是2017年的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-reputation-album-review-2158267-2158267">声誉</a>”，仅在发行几周后才能流媒体。</p><p>现在，她和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">猫王埃尔维斯·普雷斯利（Elvis Presley）</a>一起脖子，她也拥有13张英国第一张专辑。在她面前的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>，他们有14岁，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）</a>和甲壳虫乐队（Robbie Williams）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">甲壳虫乐队（Beatles）</a>共同获得了13位。 </p><figure id="attachment_3825870" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825870" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825870" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_taylorswift_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_taylorswift_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_taylorswift_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_taylorswift_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_taylorswift_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_taylorswift_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_taylorswift_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825870" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift</figcaption></figure><p>近年来，Swift在乙烯基销售方面打破了许多记录。她的第11张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">折磨诗人》部门</a>在售出112,000 lps（通过<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-best-selling-vinyl-albums-and-singles-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>官方排行榜公司</i></a>）之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/these-were-the-uks-best-selling-vinyl-albums-and-singles-of-2024-3825959">在2024年的黑胶唱片专辑榜上</a>名列前茅。在本世纪发行的第一年，没有其他专辑改变了这么多副本，其中66,000张销量在第一周进行。</p><p>它标志着连续第三年，斯威夫特在英国的乙烯基专辑排行榜上名列前茅 -  2023年，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">1989年（泰勒的版本）</a> ”是第一年，而“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-midnights-review-3332805">午夜</a>”在2022年排名第一。</p><p>这两张<a href="https://www.nme.com/review