弗雷亚·艾伦（Freya Allan）饰演玛丽安·菲斯特（Marianne Faithfull https://www.nme.com/news/film/freya-allan-to-star-as-marianne-faithfull-in-zaida-bergroth-directed-biopic-marianne-3838386?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=freya- Allan-to-Star-As-Marianne-Faithfull-in-Zaida-Bergroth-tiriphiphipicic-biopic-mariannePoppy Burton Sun, 16 Feb 2025 08:43:54 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3838386 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Marianne Faithfull和Freya Allan" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>传记片将绘制已故歌手的“从1960年代最亮的灯光到她的“辉煌的凤凰般的上升与复兴”）的“过山车骑行”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/freya-allan-to-star-as-marianne-faithfull-in-zaida-bergroth-directed-biopic-marianne-3838386">弗雷亚·艾伦（Freya Allan）的邮报（Freya Allan）饰演扎伊达·贝格罗斯（Zaida Bergroth）指导的传记“玛丽安（Marianne）”的玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Marianne Faithfull和Freya Allan" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-freya-allan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><em>巫师</em>明星弗雷亚·艾伦（Freya Allan）将在即将到来的扎伊达·贝格罗斯（Zaida Bergroth）指导的传记片<em>《玛丽安》（Marianne）</em>中扮演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marianne-faithfull">玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/marianne-faithfull-obituary-sixties-icon-broken-english-3834011">Marianne Faithfull，1946  -  2025年：抗矛盾的60年代偶像</a></strong></li></ul><p>Faithfull是1960年代摇摆的伦敦艺术和音乐界的坚定者，成为英国入侵时代的主要女艺术家之一，并于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-as-icon-marianne-faithfull-dies-age-78-she-will-be-dearly-missed-3833293">上个月去世，享年78岁</a>。</p><p>致敬<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cosey-fanni-tutti">为</a>已故的歌手倾注，后者与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-jagger">米克·贾格尔</a>（Mick Jagger） - 基思·理查兹（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keith-richards">Keith Richards）的</a>作品“随着眼泪流逝”，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tim-burgess">布鲁尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">（Blur</a> ）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-charlatans">格雷厄姆</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/graham-coxon">·柯克森</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warren-ellis">（Graham</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-harcourt">Coxon</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德（Ronnie Wood）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-lee-curtis">杰米·李·柯蒂斯（Jamie Lee Curtis）</a> ，保罗<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Paul-McCartney">·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）</a>爵士，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/morrissey">莫里西（Morrissey</a> ）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">metallica等</a>人，以及更多人的个人致敬。</p><p>芬兰导演Zaida Bergroth（ <em>Tove</em> ）现在将指挥一部名为<em>Marianne的传记片，</em>记载了伦敦歌手的生活。该项目现在正在制作前，英国演员和音乐家Jojo Macari（<em>性教育</em>）与Jagger相连。 </p><figure id="attachment_3834023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834023" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-bettman.jpg" alt="Marianne Faithfull Mick Jagger" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-bettman.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-bettman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-bettman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-bettman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-bettman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-bettman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834023" class="wp-caption-text">伦敦的玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）和米克·贾格（Mick Jagger）。图片来源：贝特曼/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>“从舞台和屏幕的女​​演员以及米克·贾格尔的长期缪斯女友和女友到无家可归，成瘾和无知的缪斯女友，”电影的<a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/global/marianne-faithfull-mick-jagger-freya-allan-jojo-macari-iopic-zaida-bergroth-tove-1236309069/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>概要</em></a>读到，</p><p> “<em>玛丽安</em>（Marianne）将描绘玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）的过山车从她青年时代的野外最亮的灯光骑行，倒下的金女孩，然后是她杰出的凤凰般的崛起和复兴”，“将她确立为我们的伟大偶像和我们真正的艺术家之一时间。”</p><p>这部电影是由朱莉娅·泰勒·斯坦利（Julia Taylor-Stanley）制作的，他曾在一部崩溃的忠实传记片中工作 - 芬兰制片人Roosa Toivonen。一部名为<em>Faithfull</em>的传记片自2020年以来一直在生产中，但尚未完成。 2022年，担任主角的露西·博因顿（ <em>Bohemian Rhapsody</em> ） <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/lucy-boynton-marianne-faithfull-interview-bohemian-rhapsody-3204124">与<em>NME</em>谈到了有关这方面的工作</a>。</p><p>博因顿说：“玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）是一个经常向她规定的身份或代表她叙述的人。” “我认为她是一个非凡的女人，因为她从未被那稀释。她本人是如此明显，一直向我们大喊大叫她是谁。 </p><figure id="attachment_3833294" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833294" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833294" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marianne_faithfull_rip.jpg" alt="Marianne Faithfull" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marianne_faithfull_rip.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marianne_faithfull_rip-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marianne_faithfull_rip-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marianne_faithfull_rip-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marianne_faithfull_rip-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marianne_faithfull_rip-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833294" class="wp-caption-text"> 2014年11月20日在法国巴黎举行的L&#39;Olympia的Marianne Faithfull。学分：Pascal Le Segretain/法语选择/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/marianne-faithfull-obituary-sixties-icon-broken-english-3834011"><em>NME向已故歌手的</em>致敬</a>中，尼克·莱文（Nick Levine）写道：“由儿子和孙子们幸存下来的忠实时光，拥有艰难的时光和灵魂的漆黑夜晚。但是不知何故，她不安的创造精神总是占上风。</p><p> “她还是自己的神话的大师。她在2014年的歌曲“将我的爱<em>给</em>伦敦”上唱歌。 “<em>地狱的天堂，男孩，天堂到地狱</em>。”最后，她死于伦敦，被家人包围，比她以前的预期更接近天堂。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/freya-allan-to-star-as-marianne-faithfull-in-zaida-bergroth-directed-biopic-marianne-3838386">弗雷亚·艾伦（Freya Allan）的邮报（Freya Allan）饰演扎伊达·贝格罗斯（Zaida Bergroth）指导的传记“玛丽安（Marianne）”的玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
鼓声和印刷品背后的团队开设了新的南伦敦场地https://www.nme.com/news/music/team-behind-drumsheds-and-printworks-to-open-new-south-london-venue-3838379?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=team-behind-drumsheds-及打开式新的 - 新南方伦敦Max PilleySat, 15 Feb 2025 22:37:26 +0000 Music NewsNewsDanceElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3838379 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 50,000平方英尺的场地名为角落角落</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/team-behind-drumsheds-and-printworks-to-open-new-south-london-venue-3838379">Drumsheds和Printworks背后开设新南伦敦场地的邮政团队</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drum_sheds_london-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦夜总会鼓声和印刷品背后的团队宣布，他们将在伦敦南部开设一个新场地。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="920" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/printworks-massive-closing-party-was-a-farewell-to-a-capital-favourite-for-now-3439256#:~:text=Despite%20the%20gloomy%20picture%2C%20the,April%2028%2DMay%201)."><b>Printworks的大规模关闭派对是向首都最爱的告别……目前</b></a></li></ul><p>新的2,000个容量网站将被命名为“角落角”（Corner Corner Corner Corner Corner Corner），将位于罗瑟赫（Rotherhithe）萨里码头（Surrey Quays）的购物中心目前占据的空间中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/corner-corner-music-venue-canada-water-shopping-mall-b1209625.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>该标准</i></a>报道说，Southwark理事会计划委员会在2月5日的一次会议上批准了场地和活动空间的计划。该计划是由Broadwick合作的房地产开发商英国土地提交的，他们说他们希望该空间可以从2025年春季。</p><p> Corner Corner将占地50,000平方英尺，并将俯瞰加拿大码头。它将用作“文化枢纽”，并具有“协作工作空间，现场音乐和食品和饮料渠道”。它还将以伦敦最大的“室内城市垂直农场”为特色，其中农产品在整个场地的餐点中使用。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4e2.png" alt="📢" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />我们已收到Corner Corner Canada Water的规划许可，这是每个人<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SE16?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">＃SE16</a>的开创性休闲空间。 <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f37d.png" alt="🍽" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/KerbFood?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Kerbfood</a>的街头食品摊位<br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f33f.png" alt="🌿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />伦敦收获的新鲜农产品<br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3b5.png" alt="🎵" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/Broadwick_Live?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@BroadWick_Live</a>策划的Live Jazz＆DJ <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/27a1.png" alt="➡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/1DPdLlb8l2">https://t.co/1dpdllb8l2</a> <a href="https://t.co/wGFwxfzBeR">pic.twitter.com/wgfwxfzber</a></p><p> - 加拿大水总规划（@cwmasterplan） <a href="https://twitter.com/CWmasterplan/status/1887522752468263265?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年2月6日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>该网站将主持现场音乐和票务DJ活动，并计划在周末凌晨3点开放直到凌晨3点，但要获得许可许可，尽管英国土地表示他们不打算举办常规的深夜活动。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/londons-drumsheds-to-enforce-new-safety-measures-licence-review-crowd-complaints-3827186">在许可证审查和人群投诉后，最近允许鼓声保持开放</a>，但已被指示执行新的安全措施。据报道，托特纳姆热刺的场地在去年有一系列严重事件在该场所发生的一系列严重事件后有丢失许可证的风险。</p><p>呼吁进行紧急许可审查，以追随一名27岁男子的死亡，该男子于10月12日参加了鼓声活动。该事件被认为与毒品有关（按照<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/drumsheds-club-tottenham-licence-stabbing-drug-deaths-b1201295.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>标准</i></a>）。 12月7日，一名29岁的妇女在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bicep">二头肌</a>在Drumsheds举行的Hydra表演后也死于医院，警方认为这也与吸毒有关。</p><p>同时，Printworks <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/printworks-massive-closing-party-was-a-farewell-to-a-capital-favourite-for-now-3439256">在去年5月关门</a>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/printworks-receives-planning-consent-for-redevelopment-an-extremely-positive-moment-for-londons-nightlife-3797389">似乎将返回</a>。 2022年，Southwark Council批准了将其转变为办公室街区的计划，但夜间工业协会在9月表示，该场地已获得重建计划的计划同意。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/team-behind-drumsheds-and-printworks-to-open-new-south-london-venue-3838379">Drumsheds和Printworks背后开设新南伦敦场地的邮政团队</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
